==English==

===Adjective===
'''jussive'''
# ''([[grammar]], of a verb):'' inflected to indicate commands, permission or agreement with a request.
#: The [[w:Jussive mood|jussive mood]] is similar to the [[cohortative]] mood, except that it also applies to verbs in the [[second person|second]] and [[third person]]. Although the jussive mood is absent from English, it is present in [[Arabic]] and [[Esperanto]].

